&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Believes good developers have acquired humility. The field of development is large and wide and is still developing at a rapid pace.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Some Stack Overflow users appear to go around telling others "you're wrong, this is useless, this is an eyesore". Like in a religion you have your individuals attempting to puff their feathers by denigrating others. These people are fake.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to know if someone is a cowboy? Pretty simple: if they keep shouting out "regular expressions are bad, XML parsers are good" then you know they have almost no real experience in industry. Send them and their 10 gallon hats, boots, and spurs back on the high horses they came riding in on.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A good answer is one that a) answers the question asked, b) provides explanation behind the answer, and c) is delivered in a timely fashion.&lt;/p&gt;
